@startuml auth-flow
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Segoe UI
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #4A90D9
    ActorBorderColor #4A90D9
    LifeLineBorderColor #4A90D9
    ParticipantBorderColor #4A90D9
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF4FF
}

title Authentication Flow — JWT + Refresh Token

actor "User" as User
participant "Web App\n(React SPA)" as Web
participant "API Server\n(OpenIddict)" as API
database "Redis\n(token blacklist)" as Redis
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Sign In ==

User -> Web: Enter email + password
Web -> API: POST /auth/token\n{email, password}
API -> DB: Validate credentials\nLook up org_id, roles
API --> Web: 200 OK\n{access_token (JWT, 15min),\nrefresh_token (opaque, 7d)}
Web -> Web: Store access_token in memory\nStore refresh_token in httpOnly cookie

== Authenticated Request ==

User -> Web: Navigate / perform action
Web -> API: GET /workflows\nAuthorization: Bearer {access_token}
API -> API: Validate JWT signature\nExtract org_id, user_id, roles\nSet tenant context (search_path)
API --> Web: 200 OK + data

== Silent Token Refresh ==

note over Web: At 80% of access_token TTL (~12 min)

Web -> API: POST /auth/refresh\n(refresh_token via httpOnly cookie)
API -> DB: Validate refresh token\n(not expired, not revoked)
API -> DB: Rotate refresh token\n(old token invalidated)
API --> Web: 200 OK\n{new access_token, new refresh_token}
Web -> Web: Replace access_token in memory

== Sign Out ==

User -> Web: Click "Sign Out"
Web -> API: POST /auth/signout\n(refresh_token via cookie)
API -> Redis: Add access_token JTI to blacklist\n(until expiry)
API -> DB: Revoke refresh token
API --> Web: 200 OK
Web -> Web: Clear access_token from memory\nRedirect to /sign-in

@enduml
